title: Top 9 Best SAW Characters #5 | SAW-Tober 2020
author: Reel Talk
comment: Easily the best part of Jigsaw
I want to see more of her

She definitely has the potential to be one of the best Saw characters, but I don't think we've seen enough of her to put her on the list yet. Hopefully we see more of her in future films. I'd like to see her be recruited as a Jigsaw killer, or start her own copy cat Jigsaw group. Either way, I hope she puts Logan in a test to teach him how it's done properly.
I’m gone build up a ginormous watch streak until I don’t know but mark my words  you will see my comment every video until I stop
